data.description: PLEASE STOP WHAT YOU ARE DOING; and check out this 6-bedroom, 4-full bathroom residence boasting an expansive 3308 square foot of living space. Situated in the heart of Rockville; the Covered Bridge Capital of the World! Recent updates include two bathrooms, kitchen enhancements and a newer roof. The home includes two furnaces and two central air systems. Outside you will enjoy the sizeable front yard, fenced in back yard, and two-car detached garage. This home offers so many options- call your favorite realtor today to schedule a showing.
